data.Name: Doctor Who
data.Bio: This is not an artist, but appears here due to incorrectly tagged soundtracks. If this non-artist appears in your charts, do last.fm and yourself a favour. Fix your tags by putting the actual artist name in the artist field. The easiest way is to use MusicBrainz Picard. Songs for the new series revival are composed by Murray Gold and the original theme song was performed by Delia Derbyshire and the BBC Radiophonic Workshop. Read more on Last.fm
